Property Documentation

- (BOOL) cleanupBodyDependencies [read, write, assign]

Setting this to YES/TRUE will also free contraints connected to a free'd shape

- (cpFloat) constantDt [read, write, assign]

If this is set to anything other than zero, the step routine will use its value as the dt (constant)

- (id<cpConstraintCleanupDelegate>) constraintCleanupDelegate [read, write, retain]

This will be called from all methods that auto-free constraints dependent on bodies being freed

- (cpVect) gravity [read, write, assign]

- (cpSpaceHashIterator) iterateFunc [read, write, assign]

- (BOOL) iterateStatic [read, write, assign]

The dt value that was used in step last

- (BOOL) rehashStaticEveryStep [read, write, assign]
